	"description": "This post is originally from www.jaredwolff.com\n[https://www.jaredwolff.com/how-to-use-particles-powerful-bluetooth-api/]\n\nI was defeated.\n\nI had spent the whole night trying to get a Bluetooth Low Energy project\nworking. It was painful. It was frustrating. I was ready to give up.\n\nThat was during the early days of Bluetooth Low Energy. Since then it&#x27;s gotten\neasier and easier to develop. The Particle Mesh Bluetooth Library is no\nexception.\n\nIn this walkthrough, i&#x27;ll show you how to use Particle",
